{"tid":1693030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建立民主經濟圈嘅同時要建立民主工會","createTime":"2019-11-04T11:19:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T05:42:12.000Z","uid":35136,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"aee921f938e569e480bd2d5f3dafda87bfb4f0ee","tid":1693030,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:19:50.000Z","msg":"之前開過post但個名改得衰 開過<br />\n呢一輪好多人講三罷 但點解好似冇聲氣<br />\n係因為香港一直都冇工會<br />\n個個都驚去到最後得自己一個罷<br />\n做咗出頭鳥就被人針對<br />\n但睇下其他國家係點搞罷工<br />\n係工會號召<br />\n透過工會知到有幾多個人同你一齊罷<br />\n如果有手足被針對被停職被炒<br />\n工會籌錢接濟<br />\n有咗呢個後盾先會有更安心咁企出嚟罷工同抗爭<br />\n85罷工好多打工仔都可能圍內有TG group 但太散<br />\n而家將呢班人用工會制度團結一齊<br />\n唔同行業嘅人想夾埋一齊 又可以有個工會渠道知道點聯絡<br />\n<br />\n而成立工會唔難 睇下職工盟個懶人包<a href=\"https://www.hkctu.org.hk/zh-hant/unionsforHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkctu.org.hk%2Fzh-hant%2FunionsforHK&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=18f4126e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkctu.org.hk/zh-hant/unionsforHK</a><br />\n只要一隻領頭羊 (好大可能會被人針對)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkctu.org.hk/zh-hant/unionsforHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkctu.org.hk%2Fzh-hant%2FunionsforHK&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=18f4126e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkctu.org.hk/zh-hant/unionsforHK</a><br />\n有七個人寫個會章<br />\n就可以申請<br />\n一間黃店入面嘅員工已經可以組一個工會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n舊post十一哥巴打提到<br />\n如果成立咗700個工會，選委會就會有60席勞工界，立法會就有3席勞工界<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每個工會7個人，只要4900個人立即行動，就得？？<br />\n<br />\n咁簡單，點解一直都唔做？<br />\n<br />\n各位和理非 咁低成本 唔係唔做呀嘛"},{"pid":"d31a4998b28c1648970e50f7f6a7c7cca12518bc","tid":1693030,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:20:40.000Z","msg":"[舊post]建立咗黃色經濟圈 係時候要黃色工會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1690035\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1690035</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1341b1674ada540354cb1524a14f8628e8f16def","tid":1693030,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:21:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a663c28f62da5b747779e41f4e556f5ff36a06","tid":1693030,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:22:59.000Z","msg":"和理非做嘢呀"},{"pid":"41f499cc02201e0398482392c656b46dcdee0b08","tid":1693030,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:25:29.000Z","msg":"文宣做都入嚟諗諗點spread開呢個idea"},{"pid":"a320cab9cba9584a1175da37dbf6c80d21e8128b","tid":1693030,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:26:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff1af5fd8af0b73ae85d721b2edd9598532ba1f3","tid":1693030,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:32:11.000Z","msg":"冇人理"},{"pid":"f18872f06eeed8956f6bedd2140e52aedfe89a63","tid":1693030,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:35:05.000Z","msg":"點解TVB仲咁撚串？因為狙擊Group 得個6千人follow，我今晚要見到過萬（2）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1693046\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1693046</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ce131605077db27ada974a147942466e41f5e612","tid":1693030,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:35:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9d7317032c98409e194020a33f8565cb916541","tid":1693030,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:37:30.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"bc3b77bbf968a9a6295f1c0bd06491a48ee4ca3f","tid":1693030,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:42:00.000Z","msg":"組織工會 全港罷工"},{"pid":"1a0b3b5446ae7f1cba415dbef5c40b79cbc85ea9","tid":1693030,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:44:49.000Z","msg":"組織工會 全港罷工"},{"pid":"6168b6b63e8c2b83fad8c71700d2e18e60498df5","tid":1693030,"uid":165683,